s.\n\nI also enjoy dancing (salsa, kizomba, etc), photography, art, and poetry. I\'m a pretty relaxed person, I like to keep myself busy during the day and focus on self-improvement, but I can always enjoy a drink and some social time at night. \n\nI\'ve lived in the city my entire life so I am familiar with the clubs, venues, bars, etc. If this is something you would like to check out I could always make suggestions.'),(16912440,22,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/16912440','Meaghan',''),(16922109,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/16922109','Vanessa',''),(16938558,16,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/16938558','Rex',''),(17000652,12,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/17000652','Richard',''),(17010369,11,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/17010369','B.J','He is the CTO of a startup here in Boston. She does Business Development for a pharmacology eLearning company. We both love this area of Boston. Things we enjoy are: traveling, trying new food, photography, picnics in parks (charcuterie and wine!), reading, visiting family and fishing. \n\nAs guests and as hosts, we try to be considerate, clean, and communicative.'),(17045533,15,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/17045533','Lilly',''),(17102895,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/17102895','Tareq',''),(17109361,24,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/17109361','Molly',''),(17177989,30,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/17177989','Ai-Ying',''),(17194624,11,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/17194624','Bernie',''),(17219748,10,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/17219748','Cecilie','Norwegian migrated to Boston where I live with family and dogs.  Enjoy urban living and spending time in the beautiful New Hampshire country side + some international travel when the opportunity arise.'),(17288874,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/17288874','Joseph','I\'ve