US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24196977','Jenny',''),(24257739,29,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24257739','Emery','Hi! My name is Emery. I will be happy to have you here!'),(24273802,12,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24273802','Eris',''),(24293931,8,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24293931','Kristin','Hi fellow airbnb-ers! I grew up in Boston and went to Umass. I work for an international publisher doing ad sales and love it. I moved to Hoboken NJ (just outside of NY) for a few years then moved to San Diego CA for over 3 years. For fun I love to travel and see new cities, find hidden gem restaurants, have wine, hike, do yoga, bike, beach it,  treat myself to some shopping. At home I have a little 4 pound Morkie named Charlie. He doesn\'t travel with me though, but I love dogs! (Allergic to cats) Looking forward to making some new friends during my travels!'),(24294559,24,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24294559','Suman','Hi there, my name is Suman and I have been living in boston from last 10 years! Spring and fall are my two favorite seasons. I love reading, listening to music ( all kind of music :) depends on my mood).'),(24337472,2,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24337472','Julie + Seven','We are 2 women, our 21 yo son who is home from college during the summer months, a dog and 2 cats. Some of our favorite things to do are watch movies, go for long walks, read, and eat good food. If there\'s any major sporting event going on, you\'ll probably find us watching it with friends in the living room, and are welcome to join us!'),(24361937,12,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24361937','Carolyn','I\'m a wellness professional, yoga instructor, and avid traveler with a graduate degree in Social Justice. I am so grateful for all of the amazing people I have met on my travels who have hosted me, helped to keep me safe on my journey, have graciously introduced me to their towns and cities, and I hope to do the same for those staying with me.\n\nA lot of my immediate network here consists of creative artists, musicians, entrepreneurs, educators and change-makers, all of whom value the richness and diversity of our community and are passionate about making it a welcoming, supportive, and thriving place to live.  \n\nI\'m passionate about building the global community through cultivating relationships and expanding perspectives; and permaculture, international music and yoga festivals, rock climbing, surfing, nature, and all of the beautiful and humbling facets of life.'),(24456619,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24456619','Justin',''),(24545104,8,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24545104','Maira',''),(24559114,14,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24559114','Nicole',''),(24567367,30,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24567367','Julien','I\'m 24 years old Finance student, currently living to Paris.'),(24584254,30,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24584254','Ak','Hi my name is Abdul Karim (everyone calls me AK) \nI love to travel and play sports\nMy passion is investing in stock markets \nI am married'),(24584716,2,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24584716','Miriam','I am committed to provide excellent service and make you feel safe and secure in a place that you can call home!'),(24587960,22,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24587960','Sun Young',''),(24593919,2,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24593919','Minor',''),(24595754,11,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/24595754','Paris','I am a working architect in the city which I wouldn\'t trade for anything! My loft and lifestyle tends to reflect that. I enjoy exploring cities and immersing myself into the culture. I am very active between work, exercise, clubs, and socializing. I live a healthy lifestyle and keep my space clean and tidy. \nI enjoy playing Boston tour