ial tour through South Boston where are also famous gangs in the past and create the theater. Your stay will contribute to make my dream truth and present. I am looking forward to meet you.'),(26164941,10,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26164941','Paul','Lived in Boston for 10 years, work in the city. Love to travel and all things Boston. My wife and I have a great condo and would love to have you enjoy it too!'),(26223574,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26223574','Artur',''),(26268405,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26268405','Amanda','Hi! I\'m a vegetarian teacher who is a bit obsessed with traveling. Je parle fran√ßais y tambi√©n hablo espa√±ol.\n\nI used to be a CouchSurfing host, but when I came to Cambridge my rent quintupled, so I can\'t afford that anymore :) but I still like the CS spirit: having drinks/meals with guests if they are up for it, or giving each other some space if you need to take it easy.'),(26303242,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26303242','Mark And Ashley',''),(26345165,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26345165','Patrick',''),(26347507,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26347507','Meredith',''),(26379614,10,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26379614','Kimberly',''),(26413047,8,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26413047','Andrew',''),(26420664,29,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26420664','Michael',''),(26510042,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26510042','Ruth',''),(26648875,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26648875','Echo','I\'m a girl from China, currently study in Boston for my master degree, I really like traveling. Especially, try the different food and enjoy the local life. That\'s the reason I come to Airbnb. I\'m new here. Want to know more about your stories.'),(26704689,24,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26704689','Mac','I grew up in Colorado, moved to Cambridge to attend MIT, moved away to London and various places, now back in Boston. My partner and I own a few buildings.. I also now work in the commercial real estate business.'),(26734256,24,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26734256','Mike',''),(26754605,30,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26754605','Katia',''),(26766201,13,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26766201','Alex','Welcome to our page! My name is Alex, and I, along with my partner Wayne, hope that we can provide you with an AirBnB experience that exceeds your expectations. Both young professionals enjoying Boston, we love to try new bars and restaurants, go hiking, and meet new people. \n\nAbove all, we would like you to feel at home in our apartment and in Boston. Whether that means directing you to any attractions or hotspots, spending time together in the apartment, or completely staying out of your way is up to you! Let us know how we can make your trip the best that it can be.'),(26853841,24,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26853841','Ashley','We own several properties around the Boston area and love showing people around and giving recommendations on what to do and see.  We hope that you enjoy your stay with us in the heart of the city.'),(26873897,30,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26873897','Vincent',''),(26956083,30,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26956083','Todd','I\'m a professional designer and house renovator, and I meticulously renovated my house in the past several years.  I\'m happy to host people from all over the world (I travel a good amount myself), and provide you with a comfortable place to stay with all the luxuries of a nice hotel in the comfort of a newly renovated home.'),(26985683,39,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/26985683','Keith',''),(27015747,10,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/27015747','Ashley  &  Dennis',''),(270