l.'),(30658962,11,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/30658962','Marlo','I\'m originally from Detroit, moved to Boston to go to law school and never left.  Today I own an integrated marketing firm with offices in Boston and New York. Many of our clients are in the hospitality business, which means I am definitely in the know about the restaurant/bar scene and am happy to make recommendations and even do some VIPing if appropriate!\n\nI lived in this apartment for years. I know you\'re not supposed to get attached to real estate, but I can\'t help it, I love it!  It\'s literally in the heart of one of Boston\'s most coveted neighborhoods, with everything literally steps from your front door. If you are the kind of person who wants to experience the hustle and energy of Boston, this is your place!'),(30679372,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/30679372','Khaled','I\'m a graduate student at NEU, i\'ve been living here for 11 months, this is my last month in this apartment and I decided to AirBnB it since I barely stay home. I\'m a very friendly person, if you need anything in Boston, I would be more than happy to help.'),(30708464,30,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/30708464','Sean',''),(30905023,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/30905023','Kierstyn',''),(30979867,3,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/30979867','Solntse','I am a budget traveller. I rent on airbnb and hence I decided to rent my property on airbnb as well. \n\nAmong the places I have visited, My favorite is washington dc in US, barcelona in europe and kerala in India. \n\nIn boston, my favorite place is the walkway around charles river.'),(30988954,30,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/30988954','Lauren','Junior in college, youthful and vibrant, occasionally gloomy (for academic reasons yeah), aspiring librarian, try to read and write more often'),(31021638,10,1,'MA','US','https://www.airbnb.com/users/show/31021638',